'''塞繆爾·薩姆-蘇馬納'''（Samuel Sam-Sumana，{{bd|1962年|4月7日|||catIdx=S}}）是[[塞拉利昂|塞拉利昂]]的一名政治人物，2007年擔任塞拉利昂副總統至2015年3月被解職。原屬全國人民大會的他於2007年總統選舉夥拍該黨總統候選人[[欧内斯特·巴伊·科罗马|欧内斯特·巴伊·科罗马]]角逐，擊敗[[塞拉利昂人民黨|塞拉利昂人民黨]]對手成功當選，同年9月17日就職。薩姆-蘇馬納和科羅馬於2012年選舉成功連任。

薩姆-蘇馬納曾經擔任當地聯合鑽石開採公司（United Diamond Mining Company）的董事總經理，及美國鑽石開採公司C-12國際（C-12 International）的地區經理。<ref name=statehouse>{{Cite web |url=http://www.statehouse.gov.sl/index.php/the-vice-president |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-03-15 |archive-date=2017-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171007110940/http://www.statehouse.gov.sl/index.php/the-vice-president |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=standardtimespress>{{Cite web |url=http://standardtimespress.org/?p=1202 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-03-15 |archive-date=2013-07-17 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130717085549/http://standardtimespress.org/?p=1202 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

薩姆-蘇馬納是[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]，科諾族人，<ref name=standardtimespress/>在美國取得[[管理資訊系統|管理資訊系統]]理學士學位。<ref name=statehouse/>

2015年3月6日，薩姆-蘇馬納被執政的全國人民大會驅逐出黨。<ref>salonemonitor.net [http://www.salonemonitor.net/vice-president-sam-sumana-expelled-from-the-ruling-apc-party/ Sam-Sumana expelled from the ruling All People's Congress party] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150317004757/http://www.salonemonitor.net/vice-president-sam-sumana-expelled-from-the-ruling-apc-party/ |date=2015-03-17 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.voanews.com/content/sierra-leone-ruling-party-expels-vice-president-sam-sumana/2671404.html VOA News] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150308060037/http://www.voanews.com/content/sierra-leone-ruling-party-expels-vice-president-sam-sumana/2671404.html |date=2015-03-08 }}</ref><ref>[http://en.starafrica.com/news/sleones-ruling-party-expels-vice-president.html starafrica.com] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402121211/http://en.starafrica.com/news/sleones-ruling-party-expels-vice-president.html |date=2015-04-02 }}</ref>該黨的全國顧問委員會指控薩姆-蘇馬納提交關於他的碩士學歷的虛假資料。他也被指在國內煽動政治暴力，並企圖另建新政黨。<ref>[http://theafricapaper.com/2015/03/07/sierra-leones-ruling-party-expels-self-quarantined-vp/ theafricapaper.com] {{Wayback|url=http://theafricapaper.com/2015/03/07/sierra-leones-ruling-party-expels-self-quarantined-vp/ |date=20220127074931 }} 2015/03/07</ref>薩姆-蘇馬納在3月14日表示他已向當地的美國大使館尋求庇護。總統科羅馬於3月17日解除他的副總統職位。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.statehouse.gov.sl/index.php/press-release/1189-sierra-leone-government-office-of-the-president-press-release |title=SIERRA LEONE GOVERNMENT Office of the President PRESS RELEASE |publisher=Office of the President, Sierra Leone Government |date=2015-03-17 |accessdate=2015-03-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321030551/http://www.statehouse.gov.sl/index.php/press-release/1189-sierra-leone-government-office-of-the-president-press-release |archivedate=2015-03-21 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-31941025 |title=Sierra Leone VP Samuel Sam-Sumana sacked |work=BBC News |date=2015-03-18 |accessdate=2015-03-18 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202181801/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-31941025 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

